**Step 4 — Run to verify PASS:** `pnpm --filter @ax/auth-better test -- --run src/__tests__/session-bridge.test.ts`. Expected: PASS.

Also run `pnpm --filter @ax/auth-better exec tsc --noEmit` (or `pnpm --filter @ax/auth-better build`) to confirm the new file type-checks cleanly (the `APIError` import especially).

